---
interface Props {
  isScarSite?: boolean;
}

const { isScarSite = false }: Props = Astro.props;
if (!isScarSite) {
  return null;
}
---

<style>
  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
  }
  th,
  td {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--bulma-border);
    padding: 0.15rem 1rem;
  }
</style>
<h3 class="title is-4">Ghostly Echoes</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>d20</th>
      <th>Ghostly Echo</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr
      ><td>1</td><td
        >A Velari scholar hurriedly scribbles arcane symbols into the air—the
        runes hang glowing for a moment before she vanishes.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>2</td><td
        >A council of Velari, robed and radiant, argue soundlessly over a
        crystalline device that shatters into fragments mid-discussion.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>3</td><td
        >A young Velari child reaches up toward a drifting shard of light,
        laughing—until both child and light blink out of existence.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>4</td><td
        >Workers and servitors scramble along glowing conduits, trying to
        stabilize them. A ripple of distorted time freezes them mid-motion.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>5</td><td
        >A procession of Velari pilgrims, heads bowed, move through a field of
        luminous crystal flowers—the flowers wilt as the pilgrims fade.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>6</td><td
        >A fragment of a great ritual: a group of Velari channel magic toward a
        massive crystal pylon, their faces straining with effort. Mid-ritual,
        they disintegrate like dust on the wind.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>7</td><td
        >Velari defenders in crystalline armor rush into battle against a foe
        the party cannot see. Their weapons pass harmlessly through the air
        before both sides dissolve.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>8</td><td
        >A marketplace scene: Velari merchants trade glittering artifacts and
        crystalline goods, chatting and smiling, oblivious to the slow crack
        forming in the sky overhead.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>9</td><td
        >A Velari musician, floating just above the ground, plays an instrument
        of light and sound. As the melody crescendos, the musician flickers out
        like a dying star.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>10</td><td
        >An entire Velari city vista appears—towers of light, flowing crystal
        roads, flying constructs—then breaks apart like shattered glass in a
        silent explosion.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>11</td><td
        >A Velari family shares a meal at a floating table set with crystalline
        dishes. A child laughs, spilling a drink that never hits the floor.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>12</td><td
        >Two Velari artisans gossip while weaving strands of glowing fiber into
        a garment. One pauses to whisper something scandalous.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>13</td><td
        >An elderly Velari slowly tends a garden of softly pulsating flowers,
        carefully trimming a withered bloom.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>14</td><td
        >Velari children chase one another around a shimmering fountain, their
        feet occasionally lifting from the ground as if forgetting gravity.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>15</td><td
        >A pair of Velari lovers, seated on a balcony high above a shining city,
        lean close, their hands barely touching.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>16</td><td
        >A group of Velari laborers push and guide translucent carts piled with
        faintly glowing stones, laughing at some shared joke.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>17</td><td
        >A Velari musician quietly plucks at a strange, luminous harp while a
        few passersby pause to listen before moving on.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>18</td><td
        >Vendors in a crystalline market call out noiselessly to customers,
        offering fruits that float gently above their stalls.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>19</td><td
        >A Velari scribe balances stacks of blank tablets while muttering under
        their breath about being late. The top tablet slides off, freezes
        midair, and vanishes.</td
      ></tr
    >
    <tr
      ><td>20</td><td
        >A group of friends play an intricate board game on a floating platform,
        laughing and shouting triumphantly—the board and pieces dissolve with
        them.</td
      ></tr
    >
  </tbody>
</table>
